column5: Executive town home near the DFW Airport features soaring 20' ceilings in the living area, a fully equipped kitchen, gas fireplace, and fenced outdoor patio. Bedroom has private bath, walk-in closet and built-in desk. Free WiFi and AirPrint laser jet printer available. Quiet subdivision and outdoor parking for two cars. Near TPC Four Seasons, Los Colinas Country Club, and just 20 min away from Cowboys Stadium and downtown Dallas.
